Interface SqlFutureList

Future<List<SqlRow>>
public interface SqlFutureList
extends Future<List<SqlRow>>

The SqlFutureList represents the result of a background SQL query execution.

It extends the java.util.concurrent.Future. 

  // create a query
 String sql = ... ;
